1. Dowlload the virtual box from this link:
https://www.virtualbox.org/wiki/Downloads

For Ubuntu:
$ sudo apt-get update
$ sudo apt-get install virtualbox-5.0
$ virtualbox

2. Download 32-bit ubuntu image for virtualBox from this link:
http://releases.ubuntu.com/14.04/

3. Open the virtualbox and follow the steps mentioned at the following links to install ubuntu at the virtual platform:
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U2LrFJnSVWU


